<lb n="0543a21" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0543a22" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 740</head>
<lb n="0543a23" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title><note n="0543013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0543013"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>頞多和多耆經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0543a24" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0543a25" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">失譯<note n="0543014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人〕－【宋】【元】【宮】，人＋（名）【明】</note><app n="0543014"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">&lac;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">人名</rdg></app>今附西晉錄</byline>
<lb n="0543a26" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT17p0543a2601">聞如是：</p><p id="pT17p0543a2604" place="inline">一時佛在為耶國時有多樹木處，與
<lb n="0543a27" ed="T"/>眾比丘僧俱，比丘有五百人。月十五日盛<note n="0543015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滿＝湯【宮】</note><app n="0543015"><lem wit="【大】">滿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">湯</rdg></app>
<lb n="0543a28" ed="T"/>時，夜半寂然安靜，比丘僧自相難問。時栴檀
<lb n="0543a29" ed="T"/>調弗天人，持天形狀威神光耀來，直前趣佛。
<pb n="0543b" ed="T" id="T17.0740.0543b"/>
<lb n="0543b01" ed="T"/><note n="0543016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">前以後＝至佛前已【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">前以後＝至佛前已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543016"><lem wit="【大】">前以後</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">至佛前已</rdg></app>，悉脫身上珍寶著一面，但<note n="0543017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">披＝被【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">披＝被【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543017"><lem wit="【大】">披</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">被</rdg></app>一領
<lb n="0543b02" ed="T"/>衣，前以頭面著佛足，禮畢問佛言：「諸可過去
<lb n="0543b03" ed="T"/>佛正覺弟子有經，<note n="0543018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔經〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔經〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543018"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>名頞多和多<note n="0543019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耆＋（經）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耆＋（經）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543019"><lem wit="【大】">耆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">耆經</rdg></app>，佛弟
<lb n="0543b04" ed="T"/>子今亦復說是頞多和多耆經，願佛為我說
<lb n="0543b05" ed="T"/>是經，當使弟子奉持。」佛默然不<note n="0543020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">應＋（而）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">應＋（而）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543020"><lem wit="【大】">應</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">應而</rdg></app>。栴檀調
<lb n="0543b06" ed="T"/>弗，稽首而&CB00230;坐。</p><p id="pT17p0543b0607" place="inline">佛即為比丘僧說經言：「我為
<lb n="0543b07" ed="T"/>若說頞多和多耆經，皆聽著心中，念之勿得
<lb n="0543b08" ed="T"/>忘。」</p><p id="pT17p0543b0802" place="inline">比丘言：「願佛說，我皆當受經戒。」</p><p id="pT17p0543b0814" place="inline">佛言：「布
<lb n="0543b09" ed="T"/>施有八事。何謂為八？愚癡人布施，但布施不
<lb n="0543b10" ed="T"/>知其恩善所在。既布施不達世間無有常，癡
<lb n="0543b11" ed="T"/>人持作常。世間苦無極，愚人持作樂。世間所
<lb n="0543b12" ed="T"/>有，愚人言，是我所有可常得。世間人皆顛倒，
<lb n="0543b13" ed="T"/>不淨臭處惡露，愚人用作好，不知作善得善，
<lb n="0543b14" ed="T"/>作惡得惡，愚人施與人，不知其人德深淺，持
<lb n="0543b15" ed="T"/>善心施與得道者，<note n="0543021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（其）＋福【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（其）＋福【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543021"><lem wit="【大】">福</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">其福</rdg></app>不可量。」</p>
<lb n="0543b16" ed="T"/><p id="pT17p0543b1601">佛告諸比丘：「何以知？愚人不知布施有十因
<lb n="0543b17" ed="T"/>緣。何等為十？愚人布施<note n="0543022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不知〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔不知〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543022"><lem wit="【大】">不知</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>為尊自用<note n="0543023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">所＝不【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所＝不【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543023"><lem wit="【大】">所</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">不</rdg></app>
<lb n="0543b18" ed="T"/>與者得善；愚人<note n="0543024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＋（以）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＋（以）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543024"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">不以</rdg></app>至心施與人也；愚人既施
<lb n="0543b19" ed="T"/>與人<note n="0543025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔與〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔與〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543025"><lem wit="【大】">與</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>時不敬重，不自手與，傳教人與施，
<lb n="0543b20" ed="T"/>人<note n="0543026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＋（久）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＋（久）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543026"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">不久</rdg></app>欲望其福，不即得其福者，自用<note n="0543027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忘＝亡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忘＝亡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543027"><lem wit="【大】">忘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">亡</rdg></app>其
<lb n="0543b21" ed="T"/>福；愚人施與佛辟支佛阿羅漢，不能自知其
<lb n="0543b22" ed="T"/>福大；愚人施與，不信佛、辟支佛、阿羅漢、阿那
<lb n="0543b23" ed="T"/>含、斯陀含、須陀洹，皆用為棄<note n="0543028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">損＝捐【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">損＝捐【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543028"><lem wit="【大】">損</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">捐</rdg></app>，無有後生；
<lb n="0543b24" ed="T"/>愚人施與，<note n="0543029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲但＝但欲【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欲但＝但欲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543029"><lem wit="【大】">欲但</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">但欲</rdg></app>得名字，欲使人稱譽。是為
<lb n="0543b25" ed="T"/>愚人布施。」</p><p id="pT17p0543b2505" place="inline">佛說經已，栴檀調弗，及諸比丘，皆
<lb n="0543b26" ed="T"/>歡喜，前為佛作禮。</p></div1>
<lb n="0543b27" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><title>佛說頞多和多耆經</title></jhead></juan>
